Key Takeaways from Journey Mapping Core Product Needs Candidate Dashboard Is CriticalNeeds to clearly communicate next steps, job match progress, interview outcomes, and hiring manager connections. Demo VideoAdd a short demo video explaining Sallys role, domain focus, and how it benefits users. Build Trust Through ProofShowcase testimonials and success stories from users with similar backgrounds to increase credibility. Post-Interview Engagement Add a Progress TrackerA visual indicator that shows completed steps and upcoming stages. Improve Candidate RetentionUse email, WhatsApp nudges, and small interactive updates to maintain engagement after the interview. Feedback Loop EnhancementsProvide interview feedback that includes performance summaries and human-reviewed insights on soft skills. Tools for Growth and Personalization Portfolio Linkage SupportAllow candidates to connect GitHub, Notion, Behance, and other platforms to highlight real work. Skill-Based Assessment IdeasExplore domain-relevant assessments that evaluate ability beyond past job titles or education. Content-Led EmpowermentOffer educational content like salary benchmarks, negotiation tips, and interview preparation resources. Introduce Sally Co-Pilot (Future Concept)A guidance layer that helps candidates understand the system, prepare better, and feel supported at every step. Recruiter-Side Insights Highlight Why a Candidate MatchesShow how candidates align with job descriptions (e.g., matched skills, soft skills, experience fit). Recruiter Testimonials Build ConfidenceUse hiring manager quotes and case studies to demonstrate success and attract more recruiter trust.

Key Takeaways Own the Interview Prep and Mock Interview Journeys (more interactive experience) Introduce a Smart Dashboard to organize and guide the job search where candidates can save jobs from all over the internet in our platform Work on a Candidates Dashboard with all the information about Applications, Interviews and Shortlisting (plus nudges to keep them engaged e.g. Youve completed 3/5 Application goals for the day, Offer Real-Time Resume Optimization with JD match scores Launch a Personalized AI Assistant/Co-pilot to guide users continuously Enhance Onboarding for instant value and engagement
